&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful candidates will be invited to an Assessment Day on Friday 18th December 2020 held at Bodmin. Please note this will be either a morning or afternoon session to be confirmed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for an energetic and enthusiast individual to work mainly with in the Day Resource Centre in Penzance facilitating groups and being instrumental in the delivery of services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will predominantly be delivering services in a group setting with in the Day Resource Centre but will also work with in the Community Mental Health Team working as part of the Multi Disciplinary Team delivering care to individuals with Severe and Enduring Mental Health conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMelanie RobertsJob titleClinical Support Team Manager, West and IOS LocalityEmail addressmelanie.roberts5@nhs.netTelephone number07387258748Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
